{"tid":1993492,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"3位90後成立觀塘黃店外賣平台","createTime":"2020-04-28T22:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T18:05:50.000Z","uid":145118,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b533c01cb04a2591fd3c4c7fb7b4fc717922b347","tid":1993492,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T22:25:57.000Z","msg":"【外賣平台】三位90後成立觀塘黃店外賣平台 只僱同路人：幫黃店幫手足<br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情加上不斷延長的限聚令，令一眾勇敢表明立場的黃店告急，不少手足也面臨失業。由於傳統外賣平台門檻高，即使小店想兼營外賣，也毫不容易。所以有三位90後，為觀塘區黃店寫了外賣平台Takeawayboys，僱用手足，令黃色經濟圈可在疫情下繼續發展。<br />\n<br />\n負責人Hendrick指今次成立契機，是源於他們點外賣時，發現眾多平台也沒有篩選黃店的功能：「這平台可以綜合在樓上的黃店，可能本來不起眼，客人在平台，一眼看到所有黃店。」年紀最小的AnChan，解釋整個架構的分別由Takeawayboys、黃店和手足組成：「我們請的外送員一定是手足，因為我們本來就是想幫補他們生計，亦希望能連繫黃店，整件事情就能幫助到黃店、幫到手足。」<br />\n<br />\n用法不算複雜，首先在Telegram加入他們寫的BOT（機械人），選擇餐廳之後就可以填表格選擇菜單，他們收到訂單後就會安排送外賣。目前接受外賣範圍是觀塘、秀茂坪和藍田。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘外賣仔<br />\n網址： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/takeawayboys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftakeawayboys&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=4496a83d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/takeawayboys</a> <br />\n電話：5425 5204<br />\n下單Telegram： <a href=\"https://t.me/taboys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftaboys&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=bc522743\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/taboys</a> <br />\n<br />\n小時光<br />\n地址：觀塘興業街18號美興工業大廈A座1樓C室 <br />\n電話：31882380<br />\n營業時間：12nn-9pm<br />\n詳情： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KHPNWZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KHPNWZ&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=d1093e78\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KHPNWZ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_60863126/外賣平台三位90後成立觀塘黃店外賣平台-只僱同路人幫黃店幫手足?fromSource=WEB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_60863126%2F%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%8D90%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8F%AA%E5%83%B1%E5%90%8C%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%AB%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E5%B9%AB%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%3FfromSource%3DWEB&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=b26cf156\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_60863126/外賣平台三位90後成立觀塘黃店外賣平台-只僱同路人幫黃店幫手足?fromSource=WEB</a><br />\n<br />\nTakeawayboysss FB:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=119495589720294&amp;id=109141194089067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D119495589720294%26id%3D109141194089067&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=24dce4f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=119495589720294&amp;id=109141194089067</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油！</span>"},{"pid":"516709688663adb388816e5870b8f0cac5d6052b","tid":1993492,"uid":331113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"推爆你 留名睇下其他區幾時有"},{"pid":"1e5cb5a4584c0e4490ecba56b6fcda166784aee2","tid":1993492,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T23:24:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea6379441db4963e1098ff96d4e248308a9ecfa1","tid":1993492,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T23:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5404562ff7da37aa61862fe13a84be8675aa0fe1","tid":1993492,"uid":101309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T23:50:36.000Z","msg":"擺小事光條link把撚咩 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c647deb2b55dbec95670d7f4c0eaa347759fc68d","tid":1993492,"uid":260581,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"小時光咁撚難食都share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00eec5580fb4279b5f828edbb7d9a5777bf8203","t